text: Up in Central Park is a 1948 American musical comedy movie directed by William A. Seiter and was based on the play of the same name by Herbert Fields. It stars Deanna Durbin, Dick Haymes, Vincent Price, Albert Sharpe, Tom Powers, Hobart Cavanaugh, Howard Freeman and was distributed by Universal Pictures. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1948 comedy movies Category:1940s American musical movies Category:American musical comedy movies Category:Movies based on plays Category:Movies directed by William A. Seiter
title: Up in Central Park
